@startuml
title Two Streams Over Single TCP Connection

participant "Client" as C
participant "TCP Connection" as TCP
participant "Server" as S

== Stream 1 ==
C -> TCP : Request1 Frame
TCP -> S : Forward Frame (Stream1)
S --> TCP : Response1 Frame
TCP --> C : Response1 Frame

== Stream 2 ==
C -> TCP : Request2 Frame
TCP -> S : Forward Frame (Stream2)
S --> TCP : Response2 Frame
TCP --> C : Response2 Frame

note over TCP
  Single TCP Connection
  contains multiple streams
end note

@enduml
